item.title: Papamavo
item.description: Papamavo is one of our 5th generation Ambilobe Panther Chameleon breeders from Papafee x Lokana. He has great vibrancy and a solid yellow body. His attitude is a bit more feisty than his father, but he’s calming down a bit now as he reaches adulthood. We are excited to see what he does for us!
